| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0549 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1ca6b48c-ab34-50be-862f-2f45f66469d0"
